 4. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the dog is the italian##1
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the british##1
10. the owner of the dog is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
