 7. the fan of folk is the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
