.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, police-officer, designer, entrepreneur
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, sports, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the designer is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 7. the police-officer is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
12. the software-developer is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up        | milk        |
| Job         | entrepreneur | designer       | software-developer | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | satire        | mystery    | sports      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rugby, water-polo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, scientific, sports, epic
 1. the fan of techno is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is between the australian and the polish##2
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the french##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 6. the fan of house is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 8. the polish is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
10. the australian is in an even position##4
11. the australian is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Nationality   | indonesian | polish  | french     | australian |
| Sport         | parkour    | cycling | rugby      | water-polo |
| Movie-Genre     | epic | scientific     | sports | horror       |

 